                "invention-title": [
                    "Monatomic metal-loaded composite photocatalyst as well as preparation method and application thereof",
                    "一种负载单原子金属的复合光催化剂及其制备方法和应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of catalysts, and particularly relates to a monatomic metal loaded composite photocatalyst and a preparation method and application thereof, and the preparation method comprises the following steps: (1) fully dipping a carbon nitride nanosheet into a nitrogen-containing precursor solution, and freeze-drying; (2) obtaining a carbon nitride nanosheet with a nitrogen-rich surface under the action of ammonia gas, hydrogen and inductively coupled low-temperature plasma; (3) loading a metal precursor to the surface of the carbon nitride nanosheet with the nitrogen-rich surface according to an equivalent-volume impregnation method, and then performing vacuum drying; and (4) carrying out discharge reaction under the action of hydrogen low-temperature plasma to obtain the carbon nitride composite photocatalyst containing the monatomic metal cocatalyst. The catalyst has the advantages of high yield, high monatomic metal loading rate and very good photocatalytic stability between different batches of samples, and is suitable for batch preparation in the future."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于催化剂技术领域，具体涉及一种负载单原子金属的复合光催化剂及其制备方法和应用，其制备方法包括：(1)将氮化碳纳米片充分浸渍到含氮前驱体溶液后冷冻干燥；(2)在氨气+氢气、电感耦合低温等离子体作用下得到表面富氮的氮化碳纳米片；(3)将金属前驱体按照等体积浸渍法负载到表面富氮的氮化碳纳米片表面后真空度干燥；(4)在氢气低温等离子体作用下通过放电反应，从而得到含有单原子金属助催化剂的氮化碳复合光催化剂。该催化剂具有产量高、单原子金属的负载率高、且不同批次样品之间的光催化稳定性非常好，适合于未来批量化制备。"
                }
            ]
